Global TODO 
-----------

This addin for tomboy when enabled checks every open note for the #TODO string. Every note with this string 
gets an entry in a note called "Global Todo". When the #TODO string is removed the entry is automatically 
removed.

Tomboy is a desktop note-taking application for Linux, Unix, Windows, and Mac OS X. Please refer to http://projects.gnome.org/tomboy/.

